<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Invoice {{invoiceNumber}} - Payment Due</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .invoice-details { background: white; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Invoice Payment Due</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear {{clientName}},</h2>
            <p>This is a reminder that payment for the following invoice is due:</p>
            
            <div class="invoice-details">
                <h3>Invoice Details</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Amount:</strong> ${{amount}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please ensure payment is made by the due date to avoid any late fees.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions about this invoice, please contact our accounting department.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your business!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>{{companyName}} Accounting Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
